{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData.append()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/append","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><em><code>append()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a> 接口的<code><strong>append()</strong></code> 方法 会添加一个新值到&nbsp;<code>FormData</code> 对象内的一个已存在的键中，如果键不存在则会添加该键。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>FormData.set</code></a> 和&nbsp;<code>append()</code>&nbsp;的区别在于，如果指定的键已经存在，&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>FormData.set</code></a> 会使用新值覆盖已有的值，而&nbsp;<code>append()</code> 会把新值添加到已有值集合的后面。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>提示</strong>：这个方法在&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>&nbsp;中可用。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个方法有两个版本：一个有两个参数的版本和一个有三个参数的版本。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> filename<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"append()_parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd><code>value中包含的数据对应的表单名称。</code></dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code></dt>\n <dd><code>表单的值。</code>可以是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a> 或&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> (包括子类型，如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>)。</dd>\n <dt id=\"filename\"><code>filename </code><span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>传给服务器的文件名称 (一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>), 当一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> 或&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> 被作为第二个参数的时候， <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> 对象的默认文件名是&nbsp;\"blob\"。 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> 对象的默认文件名是该文件的名称。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>注意：</strong>&nbsp;如果你指定一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> 作为数据添加到&nbsp;<code>FormData</code> 对象中，&nbsp;文件名会被放在 \"Content-Disposition\" 头部（常常会根据浏览器变化而变化）传给服务器。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>空</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>下面的代码创建了一个空的 FormData</code>&nbsp;对象：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FormData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Currently empty</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>你可以通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>FormData.append</code></a> 往对象里加入键值对：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Chris'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'userpic'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myFileInput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'chris.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>跟常规<code>表单数据一样，你可以使用同一个名称添加多个值</code> 。例如&nbsp;(为了与 PHP 命名习惯一致在名称中添加了 [])：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'userpic[]'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myFileInput1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'chris1.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'userpic[]'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myFileInput2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'chris2.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>这项技术使得多文件上传的处理更加简单，因为所得数据结构更有利于循环。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-formdata-append","title":"XMLHttpRequest Standard"}],"query":"api.FormData.append"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FormData.append","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/append/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">Using XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\">Using FormData objects</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"FormData 接口的append() 方法 会添加一个新值到 FormData 对象内的一个已存在的键中，如果键不存在则会添加该键。","popularity":0.0015,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/formdata/append","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/formdata/append/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData","title":"FormData"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/append","title":"FormData.append()"}],"pageTitle":"FormData.append() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}